author: schneiml
body:
#### PR description:

This is a small change to make the output of `cmsswSequenceInfo` more comprehensive. It still might not cover everything, but `ALCAHARVEST` is quite interesting from DQM point of view.

#### PR validation:

Tool still seems to work. No changes expected (incl. no changes to the unit test).
title: DQM: Add more ALCA steps to cmsswSequenceInfo.
